reviewText:
The 10-disc DVD collection includes over 8 hours of fun & these classic VeggieTales shows:
1. Sheerluck Holmes and the Golden Ruler
2. LarryBoy and the Bad Apple
3. Gideon: Tuba Warrior
4. Moe and the Big Exit
5. Saint Nicholas
6. Abe and the Amazing Promise
7. Pistachio
8. Sweetpea Beauty
9. Tomato Sawyer & Huckleberry Larry's Big River Rescue
10. Minnesota Cuke & the Search for Noah's Umbrella
